dari pemilu terakhir.

810
00:57:34,199 --> 00:57:36,368
Termasuk Pak Park Gwang-to,
mantan presiden.

811
00:57:42,291 --> 00:57:43,292
Apa kau terkejut?

812
00:57:46,545 --> 00:57:47,546
